OL,6,F"I'm devastated, but I believe I'm
OL,7,Fhoping that we can do it, I'm focusing
OL,8,Fon the hope, they can treat it and
OL,9,Fthey can cure it," he added.
OL,11,FHe was diagnosed just days after
OL,12,FLinda's funeral and decided to tell
OL,13,Fhis siblings individually, because
OL,14,Fthey had "been through enough."
OL,16,FLinda was first diagnosed in 2005,
OL,17,Fgiven the all-clear in 2011, but in
OL,18,F2017 was diagnosed with secondary
OL,19,Fbreast cancer. In 2020 it spread and
OL,20,Fby 2023 was in her brain.
