OL,3,CBrian Nolan reveals prostate cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis after sister Linda's death
OL,6,FThe Dublin-born singer made Blackpool
OL,7,Fher home, and her funeral was held in
OL,8,Fthe church where she married her late
OL,9,Fhusband, Brian Hudson. They were
OL,10,Fmarried for more than two decades.
OL,12,FAnne, who Linda joined on the TV
OL,13,Fseries The Nolans Go Cruising, was
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer for the
OL,15,Fsecond time in 2020 and previously
OL,16,Fsaid she is now cancer-free.
