OL,3,CBrian Nolan reveals prostate cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis after sister Linda's death
OL,6,FLoose Women star Coleen was diagnosed
OL,7,Fwith skin cancer last year and said
OL,8,Fshe was using a chemotherapy cream to
OL,9,Fremove it. Their sister Bernie died of
OL,10,Fbreast cancer in 2013 aged 52.
OL,12,FBrian said that he was referred to a
OL,13,Fgenetic department in Manchester, and
OL,14,Fit was "amazing how many people had
OL,15,Factually had cancer as some part of
OL,16,Fthe reason they died" in his family.
