OL,6,FHe said the doctors are "even thinking
OL,7,Fthat there may be a genetic mutation
OL,8,For something between the four cancers
OL,9,Fthat our families" have, which
OL,10,Fincludes breast, prostate, liver and
OL,11,Fpancreatic cancers.
OL,13,FBrian said his father "died of
OL,14,Fsystemic cirrhosis (liver damage) but
OL,15,Fhe also had liver cancer, my uncle
OL,16,Fdied of pancreatic cancer".
OL,18,FHe also said he wants to raise
OL,19,Fawareness of prostate cancer as his
OL,20,Ffriends did not known anything about
OL,21,Fthe illness.
